description:
Getting Unstuck: Day 18 - Using one or more of the and, or, and not Operators blocks, create a project that when multiple conditions have been satisfied, a secret is revealed.

@jentz has commented on my other project, with brighter stars and when I knew he was from Australia, I remembered the picture I took of wonderful Fireworks show on Sidney two years ago.
Immediately I thought about making a Firework project. I explored other Scratch projects and knew that are amazing ones. I took the idea to flash the background and a simple way of making fireworks.
I used clones to control the number and interval they happen.


Thank @unclives https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/11304/ 
@alib, now you can make your own show too! :)

