description:
@scmb1 helped me debug the repeated crashing problem - I've learned a lot about background screen refresh! When to use it! When to not! 

The scrolling platformer tutorial from @getbent was incredibly useful. This was my first project with a scrolling background that I made myself, instead of remixing. :) 

With more time, I would also have the clones move with the background...maybe something I'll implement later on a break!

